{"tid":838562,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"嘉道理農場吸糞車撞塌鐵閘 壓傷女工重創","createTime":"2018-09-27T08:13:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-27T08:16:07.000Z","uid":4876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9241418833c3caa539353274f66edd85024f8a7a","tid":838562,"uid":4876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T08:13:05.000Z","msg":"中午12時20分，警方接報大埔嘉道理農場有職員被塌下的鐵閘壓傷。救援人員到場，女傷者頭頸及手受傷，將她送往屯門醫院搶救。<br />\n<br />\n警方在場調查顯示，一部吸糞車離開嘉道理農場。現場大門鐵閘由4扇閘門組成，每邊兩扇對摺開關，每扇門高約12呎、濶約4呎。事發時傷者負責開閘讓車輛出入，不料吸糞車駛過時，將其中一扇閘門扯脫塌下打中她，並將她壓住。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180927/large/1538026528_cb80.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180927%2Flarge%2F1538026528_cb80.jpg&h=903bc3ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180927/large/1538025729_bebc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180927%2Flarge%2F1538025729_bebc.jpg&h=d364e43c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"36da4ed10bc8985d606fed944562906205c0eb97","tid":838562,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T08:16:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}